---
title: Chicken, Chickpea & Tabbouleh  Comment start Bowls with Dark Meat Chicken & Creamy Feta Dressing
description: We’re big fans of the ubiquitous “power bowl,” but we have to admit: This one’s extra special. It’s a one-bowl Middle Eastern–style feast that’s positively bursting with flavor. The base is a lemony bulgur salad with cucumber, tomato, scallion whites, and dill. On top, there’s crispy, harissa-spiced chickpeas, bell pepper, and a drizzle of creamy feta dressing. It doesn’t get much better than this!
